  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>GREED</strong> is a PSX styled FPS designed for replayability through speedrunning. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Inspired by the best shooters of the '90s and today, such as <i>DOOM</i>, <i>ULTRAKILL</i>, and the original <i>Half-Life.</i> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Watch your enemies fall to the ground and crush their skulls.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Defeat enemies big and small with your onslaught of weapons.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Replay levels to master them and achieve better times (for bragging rights).</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore multiple environments all with their own enemies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rid the world of greed and take back heaven.</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>GREED</strong> is a PSX styled FPS designed for replayability through speedrunning. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Inspired by the best shooters of the '90s and today, such as <i>DOOM</i>, <i>ULTRAKILL</i>, and the original <i>Half-Life.</i> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Watch your enemies fall to the ground and crush their skulls.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Defeat enemies big and small with your onslaught of weapons.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Replay levels to master them and achieve better times (for bragging rights).</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore multiple environments all with their own enemies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Rid the world of greed and take back heaven.</p></li></ul>",
